{"tid":1412081,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣快入] 講咗好多次要沽港股同MPF港股基金","createTime":"2019-08-05T05:22:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T04:12:44.000Z","uid":258381,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0243e0cdebabd47ce4caa80fb3b689b106098645","tid":1412081,"uid":258381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:22:16.000Z","msg":"講咗好多次叫你哋沽晒手頭上既MPF港股基金同其他香港資產<br />\n<br />\n睇下，恆指而家一個星期都跌咗2000點<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qiO19NC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqiO19NC.gif&h=4cddbf21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇返美股，標普500不斷破頂，由年頭到而家都跑贏恆指<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UJJ5R06.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUJJ5R06.gif&h=4b0d137f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日政府開記者招待會，財政司司長陳茂波都話暴徒破壞香港經濟<br />\n按季度調整嘅GDP最新一季有下跌趨勢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5zbSw3q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5zbSw3q.png&h=c11b36f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼續咁落去香港經濟真係會好差<br />\n恆指實跌穿20000點啦<br />\n<br />\n而家都唔知啲暴徒會唔會繼續咁搞落去<br />\n搞到個個都唔敢買樓，唔敢消費<br />\n都係快啲沽曬啲港股同MPF港股基金算啦<br />\n唔係就日日都畀啲暴徒搞到蝕晒啲錢<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對抗暴徒，你我有責，早日撤資港股</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c7dfa6833a88787da323552f69d7648580c36e21","tid":1412081,"uid":258381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:22:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73029ee8b9b33b70f8e2e71ff579979564f71c3","tid":1412081,"uid":258381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:25:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab70b987bd0eca6f75cb3551717d5a8fe9c9ebc","tid":1412081,"uid":258381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:29:12.000Z","msg":"真係講左好多次，唔該盡快撤資香港，保護個人資產，唔好比暴徒得逞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb97e9bfb7a9cbd708b48fb4dd4249871b73e39","tid":1412081,"uid":258381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:30:32.000Z","msg":"推到文宣入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97a37d66af6077a394287695810a84f0b3247be","tid":1412081,"uid":258381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:30:44.000Z","msg":"推到文宣入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2ade6d5bc9306289fbba4af4f648696ae38aab","tid":1412081,"uid":258381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"推到文宣入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dab47aef6d5eb144c49324a19433c3cd92e8f53","tid":1412081,"uid":88250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:34:38.000Z","msg":"Day 1已經無揀含中港股成份既基金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f204009d12689e58da8aaf0af18e8b52d739e0a9","tid":1412081,"uid":258381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:34:44.000Z","msg":"推到文宣入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820a04a063bd74a8ea377c2383c1ea8aa461f9fb","tid":1412081,"uid":258381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d73029ee8b9b33b70f8e2e71ff579979564f71c3","tid":1412081,"uid":258381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:25:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7ef8fd6176009e278ee2797d22cd3f3cb4f834","tid":1412081,"uid":258381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.